title: Did Kyle Rittenhouse Punch a Woman in This Video?
subtitle: A video of a fight in Kenosha, Wisconsin, supposedly shows the 17-year-old accused of killing two people at a protest assaulting a woman.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A video shows Kyle Rittenhouse, the 17-year-old accused of killing two people at a protest in Kenosha, Wisconsin, punching a woman.
